Sentencas: Highly porous and nano-structured electrodes for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells have been fabricated using a combustion chemical vapor deposition process.
Titulo: Novel nanostructured electrodes for solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by combustion chemical vapor deposition (CVD)

Sentencas: The composite electrodes consist of small grains, about 50 nm as shown in the Figure, have extremely high surface area, low interfacial polarization resistances, and high performance at low operating temperatures.
Titulo: Novel nanostructured electrodes for solid oxide fuel cells fabricated by combustion chemical vapor deposition (CVD)
